Title: The ultimate stats website for Top Chef
Description:
Ever wanted to see the compiled stats and facts across all 22 seasons of Top Chef? This incredible open-source project does just that, with gorgeous data visualizations that break down everything from chef jackets to challenge features. Check out this clip from the GitHub podcast to learn more about one of our favorite repos.
